channel.title: Warning to All Rsps Makers
channel.description:
Well i know this is in the wrong section But is the most one viewed Basicly in the last 4week's i have noticed Jagex is cracking down on rsps And rs bot's. i also have my email address in the pic for proof
I'm not trying to scare any one As we have all had ow in counters with jagex before but i got pummel buy loosing my rights to host a p server i can no longer do it as i'm being watched now.
this is basic a heads up on what may be to come. here are my pic's off Jagex kicking my ass.
First off my you tube Account. yes this is mine i can still use it but wish not you can message me or w/e for proof.
[IMG]http://i38.tinypic.com/23lkq6x.jpg[/img] [IMG]http://i37.tinypic.com/33tgrbp.jpg[/img] As i did have the most popular Rsps set up to tutorial on you tube with 108000 views.
RS BOT Shut down 3 Weeks ago http://rsbot.org/
And a few other pics i have CBF uploading them.
But this is mainly a heads up a for forums boards such as moparscape. im not sure if they have put a team together or some shit but they got me And im not even well known so bigger sites like r sev an mopa maybe hit. if this post is not locked i will be trying to get more info to help this community to avoid Jagex.
